tomllib.md
     1‚Üí# `tomllib` ‚Äì Tomli in the standard library
     3‚ÜíTomli was added to the Python standard library in Python 3.11.
     4‚Üí
     5‚ÜíRelevant links:
     6‚Üí
     7‚Üí- Python Issue Tracker: https://bugs.python.org/issue40059
     8‚Üí- Tomli issue tracker: https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/issues/141
     9‚Üí- Discussion on PyPA "blessing" a TOML parser and/or including one in the standard library: https://discuss.python.org/t/adopting-recommending-a-toml-parser/4068
    10‚Üí- Python Enhancement Proposal: https://peps.python.org/pep-0680
    11‚Üí- CPython pull request: https://github.com/python/cpython/pull/31498
    12‚Üí
    13‚Üí## Converting Tomli to tomllib ‚Ä¶
    15‚Üí### Sync status
    17‚Üí`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18‚Üímatches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    19‚Üí
    20‚Üí### Steps to convert
    22‚Üí- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
    23‚Üí
    24‚Üí- Remove `__version__ = ...` line from `cpython:Lib/tomllib/__init__.py`
    25‚Üí
    26‚Üí- Move everything in `tomli:tests` to `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib`. Exclude the following test data dirs recursively:
    27‚Üí
    28‚Üí  - `tomli:tests/data/invalid/_external/`
    29‚Üí  - `tomli:tests/data/valid/_external/`
    30‚Üí
    31‚Üí- Create `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib/__main__.py`:
    32‚Üí
    33‚Üí  ```python
    34‚Üí  import unittest
    35‚Üí
    36‚Üí  from . import load_tests
    37‚Üí
    38‚Üí
    39‚Üí  unittest.main()
    40‚Üí  ```
    41‚Üí
    42‚Üí- Add the following to `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib/__init__.py`:
    43‚Üí
    44‚Üí  ```python
    45‚Üí  import os
    46‚Üí  from test.support import load_package_tests
    47‚Üí
    48‚Üí
    49‚Üí  def load_tests(*args):
    50‚Üí      return load_package_tests(os.path.dirname(__file__), *args)
    51‚Üí  ```
    52‚Üí
    53‚Üí  Also change `import tomli as tomllib` to `import tomllib`.
    54‚Üí
    55‚Üí- In `cpython:Lib/tomllib/_parser.py` replace `__fp` with `fp` and `__s` with `s`. Add the `/` to `load` and `loads` function signatures.
